==English==

==Etymology==
Coined by [[podcaster]] Scott Fletcher in February 2005 when he gave up on two [[podcast]]s of his own

===Noun===
'''podfading'''  ''uncountable''
# the phenomenon of [[podcast]]s disappearing after a relatively short time

